#N canvas 120 80 1280 720 10;
#X text 30 15 PLAY multitrack synth pd~ split. Main patch keeps sequencing/voice allocation. Voices 1-6 go to pd~ A, voices 7-12 go to pd~ B. Each subprocess runs six synthvoice instances and receives synthparams messages.;
